claim.claim-text:
1. A turbine/generator system comprising:
a multispool gas turbine having a high pressure shaft and a low pressure shaft;
an inner rotor mounted on the low pressure shaft;
an outer induction rotor mounted on the high pressure shaft coaxially with and radially outward of the inner rotor; and
a stator mounted coaxially with and radially outward of the outer induction rotor.

12. A multi-rotor generator comprising:
an inner rotor mounted on a first rotating shaft configured to rotate at a first speed range;
an outer rotor mounted concentric with and radially outward of the inner rotor, on a second rotating shaft concentric with the first rotating shaft and configured to rotate at a second speed range not equal to the first speed range;
a stator mounted concentric with and radially outward of the outer rotor.
